%22%3Epost%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20hiring%20of%20Nakasone%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bcalculated%20betrayal%20to%20the%20rights%20of%20every%20person%20on%20Earth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20gone%20full%20mask-off%3A%20do%20not%20ever%20trust%20OpenAI%20or%20its%20products%20(ChatGPT%20etc)%26quot%3B%20Snowden%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsnowden%2Fstatus%2F1801792686724182242%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DNui0UmVGijsDXT2qSHv1rQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomment%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Snowden%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bintersection%20of%20AI%20with%20the%20ocean%20of%20mass%20surveillance%20data%20that's%20been%20building%20up%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%20is%20going%20to%20put%20truly%20terrible%20powers%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20an%20unaccountable%20few.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Mark%20Warner%2C%20a%20Democrat%20from%20Virginia%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Senate%20Intelligence%20Committee%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20described%20Nakasone's%20hiring%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20get.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20nobody%20in%20the%20security%20community%2C%20broadly%2C%20that's%20more%20respected%2C%26quot%3B%20Warner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F06%2F13%2Fopen-ai-security-nakasone-nsa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Axios%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENakasone's%20expertise%20in%20security%20may%20be%20needed%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20where%20critics%20have%20worried%20that%20security%20issues%20could%20open%20it%20up%20to%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20fired%20former%20board%20member%20Leopold%20Aschenbrenner%20in%20April%20after%20he%20sent%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-openai-researcher-leopold-aschenbrenner-interview-firing-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememo%20detailing%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20security%20incident%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20He%20described%20the%