ild%20of%20a%20White%20Confederate%20officer%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20an%20enslaved%20Black%20man%20who%20is%20following%20his%20Confederate%20owner%20to%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memorial%2C%20designed%20by%20the%20sculptor%20and%20Confederate%20veteran%20Moses%20Jacob%20Ezekiel%2C%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20cemetery%20in%201914%20%E2%80%94%20nearly%2050%20years%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Civil%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20depiction%20of%20%26quot%3BBlack%20Mammies%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20stereotypical%20one%2C%20where%20enslaved%20Black%20women%20were%20depicted%20as%20being%20content%20with%20their%20predicament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20Minority%20Leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdemocraticleader.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Fleader-jeffries-extreme-maga-republicans-are-trying-once-again-march-us-toward%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHakeem%20Jeffries%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20New%20York%20on%20Friday%20blasted%20the%20GOP%20lawmakers%20who%20supported%20the%20amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20tradition%20are%20extreme%20MAGA%20Republicans%20%E2%80%A6%20upholding%3F%20What%20Confederate%20tradition%20are%20you%20upholding%3F%20Is%20it%20slavery%3F%20Rape%3F%20Kidnap%3F%20Jim%20Crow%3F%20Lynching%3F%20Racial%20oppression%3F%20Or%20all%20of%20the%20above%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20a%20Capitol%20Hill%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20debate%20comes%20four%20years%20after%20the%20death%20of%20George%20Floyd%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Minneapolis%20police%20and%20the%20following%20national%20racial%20reckoning.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fgeorge-floyd-protests%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProtests%20against%20racial%20injustice%3C%2Fa%3E%20swept%20the%20country%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20many%20lawmakers%20sought%20to%20shepherd%20through%20reforms%20aimed%20at%20tackling%20racial%20discrimination%20and%20disparities%20in%20everything%