https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fpodcasts%2Fstephen-fry-red-white-royal-blue-2-prince-william-harry-1236039090%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fpodcasts%2Fstephen-fry-red-white-royal-blue-2-prince-william-harry-1236039090%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20number%20of%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20scams%20has%20grown%20by%20183%25%20so%20far%20this%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22952%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20example%20of%20a%20fake%20ad%20claiming%20to%20sell%20Ozempic%20on%20Facebook.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666b4fefed9a404d829d9f81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22538%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20example%20of%20a%20fake%20ad%20claiming%20to%20sell%20Ozempic%20on%20Facebook.%3Cp%3EMcAfee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPhishing%20scams%20targeting%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%20rose%20183%25%20from%20January%20to%20April.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESocial%20media%20sites%20like%20Facebook%20are%20hotspots%20for%20these%20scams%2C%20McAfee%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScammers%20exploit%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20these%20drugs%20to%20lure%20victims%20with%20cheap%20offers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20anyone%20knows%20a%20good%20deal%20when%20they%20see%20it%2C%20it's%20an%20online%20scammer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trendy%20weight%20loss%20drug%20Ozempic%2C%20which%20can%20cost%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20is%20an%20opportunity%20apparently%20too%20good%20for%20them%20to%20pass%20up.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20research%20released%20by%20McAfee%2C%20a%20computer%20and%20cybersecurity%20company%2C%20says%20that%20phishing%20scams%20targeting%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Econsumers%20interested%20in%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy%2C%20and%20Semaglutide%20rose%20183%25%20from%20January%20to%20April%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECriminals%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-phishing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephishing%20scams%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20trick%20people%20into%20sharing%20personal%20information.%20A%20scammer%20usually%20sends%20an%20email%20or%20some%20other%20message%20pretending%20to%20be%20a%20company%20or%20individual%20the%20victim%20is%20familiar%20with%2C%20asking%20for%20credit%20card%20info%2C%20passwords%2C%20or%20other%20sensitive%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20scams%20occur%20on%20sites%20like%20Facebook%20or%20Craigslist%2C%20where%20researchers%20said%20they%20found%20207%20phony%20postings%20advertising%20Ozempic%20in%20just%20one%20day%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Facebook%2C%20scammers%20often%20pretend%20to%20be%20doctors%2C%20claiming%20to%20hand%20out%20Ozempic%20and%20other%20drugs%20without%20a%20prescription%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20Once%20they%20contact%20potential%20victims%2C%20the%20scammers%20pressure%20them%20to%20use%20unconventional%20payment%20methods%20for%20prescription%20drugs%2C%20McAfee%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20example%20on%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20included%20a%20'Doctor%20Melissa'%20based%20in%20Canada%20who%20could%20provide%20Mounjaro%20and%20Ozempic%20without%20a%20prescription%2C%20with%20payment%20available%20through%20Bitcoin%2C%20Zelle%2C%20Venmo%2C%20and%20Cash%20App%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20are%20non-standard%20payment%20methods%20for%20prescription%20drugs%20and%20should%20be%20red%20flags%20for%20consumers.%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20studies%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbernie-sanders-ozempic-cheaper-novo-nordisk-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOzempic%20costs%20just%20%245%20to%20make%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20drug%20sells%20for%20about%20%241%2C000%20a%20month.%20This%20high%20price%20makes%20some%20consumers%20more%20eager%20to%20take%20a%20cheap%20offer%20online%2C%20McAfee%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCybercriminals%20are%20always%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20ways%20to%20make%20their%20scams%20more%20attractive%20and%20believable%2C%26quot%3B%20Abhishek%20Karnik%2C%20head%20of%20McAfee's%20Threat%20Research%20Team%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BTapping%20into%20the%20current%20craze%20for%20Ozempic%20and%20related%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20is%20one%20way%20scammers%20can%20lure%20you%20in%20through%20phishing%20emails%2C%20fake%20social%20posts%2C%20or%20ads%2C%20all%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20deal%20that%20seems%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20tips%20McAfee%20recommends%20to%20avoid%20becoming%20a%20victim%20of%20scams%20are%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20unofficial%20retailers%2C%20watch%20out%20for%20suspiciously%20low%20prices%20or%20strange%20payment%20methods%2C%20and%20watch%20for%20missing%20product%20details%2C%20such%20as%20expiration%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScam%20websites%20typically%20lack%20verifiable%20product%20information%20and%20sometimes%20are%20poorly%20designed%20with%20grammar%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20says.%20%26quot%3BPay%20attention%20to%20and%20read%20the%20fine%20print.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-recover-from-identity-theft%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyou%20fall%20victim%20to%20a%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20money%20can%20be%20difficult%20for%20law%20enforcement%20to%20recover.%20The%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20recommends%20reaching%20out%20to%20whatever%20company%2C%20bank%2C%20or%20credit%20card%20company%20helped%20you%20facilitate%20the%20money%20transfer%20to%20try%20and%20recover%20stolen%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-wegovy-scams-phishing-cyber-security-mcafee-ai-facebook-crai