%20Tax%20On%20Fuel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20government%20on%20Saturday%20hiked%20sales%20tax%20on%20fuel%20which%20will%20make%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20costlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20sources%2C%20petrol%20will%20now%20go%20up%20by%20Rs%203%20and%20diesel%20by%20Rs%203.5%20per%20litre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Finance%20Department%2C%20the%20government%20has%20hiked%20sales%20tax%20on%20petrol%20by%203.92%20percentage%20points%2C%20from%2025.92%20to%2029.84%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20diesel%2C%20the%20hike%20is%204.1%20percentage%20points%2C%20from%2014.34%20to%2018.44%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20notification%20shall%20come%20into%20force%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20results%2C%20in%20which%20NDA%20got%2019%20out%20of%2028%20seats%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20with%20BJP%20winning%2017%20and%20JD(S)%20with%202.%20The%20ruling%20Congress%20in%20the%20state%20has%20won%20nine%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20aimed%20at%20resource%20mobilisation%2C%20comes%20after%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20finance%20minister%2C%20reviewed%20the%20state's%20revenue%20generation%20and%20fiscal%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20CM%20asked%20officials%20to%20work%20harder%20towards%20meeting%20revenue%20collection%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20hike%20is%20expected%20to%20generate%20Rs%202%2C500-Rs%202%2C800%20crore%20during%20the%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20government%2C%20Karnataka%20BJP%20president%20B%20Y%20Vijayendra%20urged%20the%20chief%20minister%20to%20roll%20back%20the%20hike%20in%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20prices%2C%20as%20he%20threatened%20a%20state%20wide%20protest%20by%20the%20party%20on%20Monday%2C%20at%20all%20district%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFaced%20by%20defeat%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20accept%20that%20the%20financial%20situation%20of%20the%20state%20has%20deteriorated%2C%20but%20the%20hike%20in%20fuel%20prices%20proves%20it.%20The%20government%20is%20unable%20to%20run%20the%20administration%20because%20of%20guarantees%2C%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20get%20proper%20resources....The%20government%20should%20withdraw%20this%20decision%20(of%20fuel%20price%20hike)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20Assembly%20R%20Ashoka%20said%20this%20%26quot%3Banti-people%26quot%3B%20Congress%20government%20is%20taking%20revenge%20on%20Kannadigas%20for%20voting%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20emptied%20the%20state's%20coffers%20with%20its%20unscientific%20guarantee%20schemes%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20is%20going%20to%20fill%20the%20treasury%20by%20taxing%20the%20Kannadigas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20'X'%2C%20adding%20that%20with%20this%20hike%20the%20government%20has%20%26quot%3Bcut%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20public%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20has%20set%20aside%20Rs%2052%2C009%20crore%20for%20his%20government's%20flagship%20five%20guarantee%20schemes%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20government's%20five%20guarantee%20schemes%20are%20-%20200%20units%20of%20free%20power%20to%20all%20households%20(Gruha%20Jyoti)%2C%20Rs%202%2C000%20monthly%20assistance%20to%20the%20woman%20head%20of%20every%20family%20(Gruha%20Lakshmi)%2C%20payment%20of%20cash-in-lieu%20of%20the%20additional%205%20kg%20of%20rice%20to%20every%20member%20of%20a%20BPL%20household%20(Anna%20Bhagya)%2C%20Rs%203%2C000%20every%20month%20for%20unemployed%20graduate%20youth%20and%20Rs%201%2C500%20for%20diploma%20holders%20for%20two%20years%20(YuvaNidhi)%2C%20and%20free%20travel%20for%20women%20in%20public%20transport%20buses%20(Shakti).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718462700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fglne16o8_petrol-fuel-generic_625x300_16_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpetrol-diesel-to-get-costlier-in-karnataka-after-hike-in-sales-tax-on-fuel-5897541%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka%20government%20on%20Saturday%20hiked%20sales%20tax%20on%20fuel%20which%20will%20make%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20costlier.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpetrol-diesel-to-get-costlier-in-karnataka-after-hike-in-sales-tax-on-fuel-5897541%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpetrol-diesel-to-get-costlier-in-karnataka-after-hike-in-sales-tax-on-fuel-5897541%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpetrol-diesel-to-get-costlier-in-karnataka-after-hike-in-sales-tax-on-fuel-5897541%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kuwait%20fire%3A%20Company%20will%20take%20care%20of%20victims'%20families%2C%20says%20NBTC%20MD%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718462654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F13%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1718258025-9229.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkuwait-fire-company-will-take-care-of-victims-families-says-nbtc-md-124061500532_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abraham%20said%20that%20his%20company%20directors%20and%20managers%20are%20currently%20visiting%20each%20and%20every%20family%20member%20of%20the%20deceased%20and%20are%20expressing%20their%20grief%22%2C%