tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-overview-search-incorrect-social-media-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20keeps%20making%20headlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20AI%20mistakes%20that%20go%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20releasing%20its%20AI%20Overviews%20feature%2C%20which%20provides%20AI-generated%20summaries%20for%20some%20search%20queries%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20page%2C%20the%20internet%20started%20buzzing%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-ai-overview-answers-pizza-glue-fix-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esearch%20engine%20recommending%20eating%20glue%20pizza%20or%20consuming%20rocks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20it%20launched%20its%20image-generation%20tool%20on%20Gemini%20and%20caused%20a%20stir%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogles-ceo-response-gemini-ai-image-controversy-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echatbot%20inaccurately%20recreated%20images%20of%20historical%20figures%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Google%20acknowledged%20the%20issue%20and%20paused%20the%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20like%20Google%20isn't%20going%20to%20pump%20the%20brakes%20anytime%20soon%2C%20though%2C%20even%20with%20the%20high-profile%20flubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20VP%20of%20Search%20Liz%20Reid%20addressed%20the%20recent%20pizza%20glue%20and%20eating%20rocks%20fiasco%20at%20a%20recent%20all-hands%20meeting%20and%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20reaffirm%20the%20company's%20AI%20strategy%2C%20according%20to%20leaked%20audio%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F06%2F13%2Fgoogle-wont-always-find-mistakes-in-ai-search-vp-reid-tells-staff.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobtained%20by%20CNBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20that%20we%20don't%20hold%20back%20features%20just%20because%20there%20might%20be%20occasional%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Rei