3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrooping%20the%20Colour%20marks%20the%20British%20sovereign's%20official%20birthday%20and%20is%20a%20minutely%20choreographed%20military%20tradition%20dating%20back%20more%20than%20two%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20starts%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%20and%20moves%20down%20The%20Mall%20to%20Horse%20Guards%20Parade%2C%20where%20King%20Charles%20will%20receive%20a%20royal%20salute%20before%20inspecting%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKing%20Charles%20was%20actually%20born%20in%20November%20but%20the%20second%20birthday%20tradition%20dates%20back%20to%20King%20George%20II%20in%201748%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20celebration%20in%20better%20weather%20as%20his%20own%20birthday%20was%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20has%20its%20origins%20in%20the%20preparations%20for%20war%2C%20where%20all%20regimental%20flags%20--%20or%20colours%20--%20were%20shown%20to%20the%20soldiers%20so%20that%20they%20would%20recognise%20them%20in%20the%20confusion%20of%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20event%20will%20include%20three%20of%20five%20military%20horses%20that%20bolted%20through%20the%20streets%20of%20central%20London%20in%20April%20after%20being%20spooked%20by%20the%20noise%20of%20building%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELondon's%20Metropolitan%20Police%20said%20it%20would%20mount%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20security%20operation%20and%20had%20been%20liaising%20with%20anti-monarchy%20group%20Republic%2C%20which%20kicked%20off%20protests%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20force%20said%20it%20had%20banned%20%26quot%3Bamplified%20sound%26quot%3B%20in%20and%20around%20the%20parade%20route%20on%20public%20safety%20grounds%20and%20to%20avoid%20disruption%20to%20the%20mounted%20regiments%20taking%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublic's%20activists%2C%20who%20huddled%20on%20a%20section%20of%20The%20Mall%20alongside%20royalists%2C%20held%20aloft%20placards%20bearing%20slogans%20including%20%26quot%3Bnot%20