ther%20players.%26quot%3B%20Imrul%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricfrenzy.com%2Farticle%2F157323%2FImrul-Kayes-hits-back-after-Sehwag%25E2%2580%2599s-harsh-comment-on-Shakib%5C%22%3ECricFrenzy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifferent%20countries'%20cricketers%20evaluate%20other%20countries'%20cricketers%20differently.%20Virender%20Sehwag%20has%20made%20such%20comments%20throughout%20his%20career.%20He%20has%20also%20made%20such%20comments%20about%20our%20country%2C%20saying%20we%20don't%20have%20an%20environment%20suitable%20for%20cricket%2C%20and%20that%20we%20don't%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20take%2020%20wickets%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20But%20we%20did%20take%20those%20wickets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Bangladesh%20cricketer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImrul%20also%20praised%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%20for%20his%20achievements%20and%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20cricketers%20should%20be%20spoken%20about%20with%20respect%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShakib%20did%20not%20become%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%20in%20one%20or%20two%20days.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20his%20career%2C%20you%20will%20see%20many%20achievements.%20He%20has%20been%20the%20number%20one%20all-rounder%20in%20all%20three%20formats%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20think%20such%20cricketers%20should%20be%20spoken%20about%20with%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718439360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F4d893n28_virender-sehwag-prediction-_625x300_27_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fyou-wont-see-sachin-dravid-ex-bangladesh-star-blasts-virender-sehwag-over-shakib-al-hasan-dig-5891069%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Bangladesh%20cricket%20team%20batter%20Imrul%20Kayes%20blasted%20Virender%20Sehwag%20for%20his%20comments%20on%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%20over%20his%20poor%20run%20of%20form%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%22%