26quot%3Bguru%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20like%20Nayanar%20and%20his%20wife%20Sarada%20Teacher%2C%20he%20had%20close%20relations%20with%20Karunakaran%20and%20his%20wife%20Kalyanikutty%20Amma%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20visited%20Nayanar's%20home%20in%20Kannur%20and%20renewed%20his%20relationship%20with%20his%20family%20members%20on%20June%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gopi%20said%20as%20he%20viewed%20Indira%20Gandhi%20as%20%26quot%3Bbharathathinte%20mathavu%26quot%3B%20(mother%20of%20India)%2C%20Karunakaran%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bfather%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20the%20state%26quot%3B%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20describing%20Karunakaran%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfather%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Kerala%20was%20not%20a%20disrespect%20to%20the%20founders%20or%20co-founders%20of%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor-turned-politician%20also%20hailed%20the%20administrative%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Congress%20veteran%20and%20dubbed%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcourageous%20administrator%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20though%20he%20had%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20visit%20the%20Murali%20Mandiram%20in%202019%20also%2C%20the%20veteran's%20daughter%20Padmaja%20Venugopal%2C%20who%20recently%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20discouraged%20him%20due%20to%20political%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Suresh%20Gopi%20also%20visited%20the%20famous%20Lourde%20Mata%20Church%20in%20the%20city%20and%20offered%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20family's%20presentation%20of%20a%20golden%20crown%20to%20the%20idol%20of%20St%20Mary%20during%20his%20daughter's%20marriage%20was%20used%20by%20his%20political%20opponents%20to%20target%20him%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20was%20not%20made%20of%20yellow%20metal%20but%20copper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gopi%20won%20the%20Thrissur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2