re%20nowhere%20close%20to%20real%20interviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20IAS%20Aaditya%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20interviewer%20panel%20comprises%20five%20experts%20in%20their%2050s%20and%2060s.%20They%20have%20a%20combined%20experience%20of%20five%20times%20our%20ages.%20Except%20for%20a%20few%20coaching%20institutes%2C%20several%20others%20make%20a%20fool%20out%20of%20aspirants%2C%20like%20asking%20them%20to%20propose%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20and%20what%20to%20do%20if%20this%20was%20their%20last%20day%20of%20life.%20Do%20not%20blindly%20rely%20on%20such%20videos.%20It%20cannot%20compete%20with%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20clearing%20Prelims%20and%20Mains%2C%20candidates%20are%20required%20to%20go%20through%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20UPSC%20(Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission)%20exam%20%E2%80%94%20the%20interview%20round.%20The%20goal%20of%20the%20interview%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281857%2Fupsc-cse-interview-topper-ias-apala-mishra-score-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonality%20test%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20to%20evaluate%20their%20aptitude%2C%20ability%20to%20interact%20with%20people%2C%20and%20interest%20in%20current%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Aaditya%2C%20who%20secured%20190%20marks%20in%20the%20interview%20round%2C%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20UPSC%20interview%2C%20and%20spare%20candidates%20from%20falling%20into%20the%20trap%20of%20mock%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20Aaditya%20is%20posted%20as%20an%20assistant%20collector%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Jharkhand.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352535%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECurrently%2C%20Aaditya%20is%20posted%20as%20an%20assistant%20collector%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20being%20a%20mischievous%20kid%20to%20an%20IAS%20officer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20was%20born%20into%20a%20humble%20family%20in%20Vishunpur%20Pakri%20village%20in%20Patna%2C%20Bihar.%20Like%20most%20kids%20his%20age%2C%20he%20says%20he%20was%20quite%20impish.%20%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20one%20of%20my%20teachers%20came%20to%20our%20home%20and%20straight%20away%20went%20to%20complain%20to%20my%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%20%3C%2Fem%3E(father).%20He%20said%20if%20I%20ever%20became%20serious%20about%20my%20studies%2C%20he%20would%20shave%20his%20moustache%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Aaditya%20went%20on%20to%20pursue%20electronics%20engineering%20from%20Lovely%20Professional%20University%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20later%20on%20pursued%20higher%20education%20in%20business%20administration%20from%20IIT%20Roorkee.%20After%20working%20for%20two%20years%20in%20a%20private%20bank%2C%20he%20eventually%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20prepare%20for%20UPSC%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20shaped%20his%20vision%20was%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20bureaucrat%20at%20IIT%20Roorkee.%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20Bihar%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20charm%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20an%20IAS%20officer.%20But%20you%20cannot%20delve%20into%20the%20service%20just%20because%20of%20the%20charm.%20I%20was%20inspired%20to%20become%20an%20IAS%20after%20speaking%20to%20a%20bureaucrat%20who%20was%20working%20with%20the%20railway%20services.%20I%20learned%20about%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20UPSC%20from%20him%20and%20my%20peers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20him%20two%20failed%20attempts%20to%20finally%20clear%20UPSC%20CSE%20in%20the%202022%20examination%20with%20an%20impressive%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2048.%20Currently%2C%20he%20is%20posted%20as%20an%20assistant%20collector%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCt689mSPpct%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCt689mSPpct%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCt689mSPpct%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Aaditya%20Pandey%2C%20IAS%20(%40aaditya.advait)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20for%20UPSC%20exam%20and%20interview%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20his%20experience%2C%20Aaditya%20shares%20five%20mistakes%20and%20learnings%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20examination%20as%20well%20as%20the%20personality%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Do%20not%20attempt%20fewer%20questions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20first%20attempt%2C%20I%20opted%20for%20only%2057%20to%2058%20questions%20whereas%2064%20to%2066%20questions%20in%20the%20second%20attempt.%20I%20missed%20the%20cut-off%20by%202.5%20marks%20in%20the%20second%20attempt.%20So%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20attempt%2084%20questions%20in%20my%20third%20attempt%2C%20which%20helped%20me%20score%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Prepare%20short%20notes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20changes%20that%20he%20made%20in%20his%20strategy%20on%20the%20third%20attempt%2C%20Aaditya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20prepared%20notes%20for%20most%20of%20the%20subjects.%20Although%20note-making%20was%20additional%20work%2C%20it%20helped%20me%20understand%20concepts%20better.%20It%20helps%20to%20save%20time%20instead%20of%20checking%20source%20material%20repeatedly.%20It%20also%20helps%20for%20effective%20revision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20two%20failed%20attempts%2C%20Aaditya%20cleared%20UPSC%20CSE%20in%202022%20with%20an%20impressive%20AIR%20of%2048.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-1718010869-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352537%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20two%20failed%20attempts%2C%20Aaditya%20cleared%20UPSC%20CSE%20in%202022%20with%20an%20impressive%20AIR%20of%2048.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20did%20not%20pressurise%20myself%20much.%20If%20I%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20study%2C%20I%20would%20sit%20in%20a%20corner%20with%20my%20coffee%20mug%2C%20close%20my%20eyes%2C%20and%20recall%20my%20notes.%20If%20I%20missed%20some%20point%2C%20then%20I%20would%20immediately%20refer%20to%20my%20notes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20suggests%20aspirants%20make%20notes%20only%20after%20first%20reading.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20make%20notes%20majorly%20for%20Acts%20and%20rules.%20You%20can%20make%20notes%20by%20summarising%20the%20topic.%20Make%20sure%20that%20you%20do%20not%20end%20up%20writing%20another%20book.%20Final%20notes%20should%20be%2033%20percent%20of%20all%20topics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Know%20your%20DAF%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20says%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fupsc-cse-how-to-fill-detailed-application-form-daf-ias-irs-ifs-officers-share-tips-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDetailed%20Application%20Form%20%3C%2Fa%3E(DAF)%20is%20very%20crucial%20for%20the%20personality%20test%20round.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20Mains%2C%20candidates%20need%20to%20fill%20out%20DAF%20which%20contains%20details%20like%20hometown%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20hobbies%2C%20and%20interests.%20Do%20not%20fill%20them%20recklessly%20as%20initial%20questions%20can%20be%20framed%20from%20DAF%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInterviews%20are%20very%20subjective.%20The%20first%20question%20asked%20in%20the%20interview%20determines%20the%20interview%20flow%20and%20whether%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20mould%20it%20in%20your%20favour.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20command%20of%20your%20DAF%2C%20then%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20sail%20through%20the%20interview%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20DAF%2C%20Aaditya%20mentioned%20listening%20to%20Ramcharitmanas%20(an%20epic%20poem%20that%20contains%20the%20deeds%20of%20Lord%20Rama)%20and%20watching%20Korean%20dramas%20as%20his%20interests.%20This%20framed%20his%20interview%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20similarities%20and%20differences%20between%20ancient%20values%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Indian%20and%20Korean%20societies.%20Another%20question%20was%20based%20on%20the%20division%20of%20Korea%20and%20its%20war%20history.%20Later%20on%2C%20we%20spoke%20on%20the%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20I%20did%20not%20mention%20in%20my%20DAF%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aaditya%20secured%20190%20marks%20in%20the%20UPSC%20interview%20round.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-1-1718002304-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352529%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAaditya%20secured%20190%20marks%20in%20the%20UPSC%20interview%20round.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20interviewer%20was%20a%20war%20veteran%20himself.%20So%2C%20you%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20interviewer%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Be%20yourself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20people%20warned%20Aaditya%20for%20his%20blunt%20and%20outrageous%20attitude.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20said%20it%20would%20cost%20me%20final%20marks%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20tone%20down%20my%20personality.%20Only%20a%20few%20mentors%20supported%20me.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about%20if%20you%20express%20yourself%20properly%20and%20your%20views%20are%20backed%20with%20logic%2C%20moral%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20legal%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20believes%20aspirants%20must%20seek%20one-on-one%20interviews%20with%20a%20known%20person%20who%20can%20really%20assess%20their%20personality%20and%20attitude%20in%20order%20to%20help%20build%20confidence%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281037%2Fhow-to-crack-upsc-interview-tips-ias-officer-twitter-personality-test%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%20i